---------------------------------------------------------------
Here are the instructions to install and run uboot recover tool:
---------------------------------------------------------------

Pyhton 2.4 has to be installed on your system. If not, take a look at here:
www.python.org/download/releases/2.4.4/

For the windows users:
Install the win32 extension package for python 2.4 (pywin32).
http://sourceforge.net/projects/pywin32/

For all users
Install the serial port package for python (pyserial).
http://sourceforge.net/projects/pyserial/

Usage
Simply connect the APF to the serial port of the host and run the uboot_recover tool.
->python uboot_recover.py
Then indicate which port is used to communicate with the APF (ttySx or COMx)
That's all
